channel.title: Annoying error "This user is already online"
channel.description: Sometimes my server will randomly decide, "what the hell, why not log every1 out and say "This user is already online!" when they try logging in. I have to restart the server which takes me off 100% and is really is annoying becuase im not on the computer all day everday to see when this happens. Anyone got any idea how to fix this? :confused:[br][br][size=1]Posted on: April 19, 2008, 11:43:08 PM[/size][hr]-.-
